title: Grateful Dead Live at Hartford Civic Center on 1988-04-04
lineage: DAT (Sony PCM-R500) > Sound Devices 744T > wav 16/44; Joe Noel Edits: Track, Flac & Pack: Wave > Audacity > flac 16/44; Checksum & tags created in xACT
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Johnny B. Goode, Good Time Blues, They Love Each Other, Queen Jane Approximately, When Push Comes To Shove, Cassidy, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Touch Of Gray, Looks Like Rain-> Truckin'-> He's Gone-> Jam-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Good Lovin'-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Hey Jude, E: U.S. Blues
